tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE public_transportation_maintenance_records (
    record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    maintenance_type TEXT,
    date_performed DATE,
    cost DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE maintenance_records (
    record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    maintenance_type VARCHAR(50),
    maintenance_date DATE,
    mechanic_name VARCHAR(50),
);

CREATE TABLE vehicle_details (
    vehicle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    manufacturer VARCHAR(50),
    model VARCHAR(50),
    year INT,
    emission_level VARCHAR(50),
);

CREATE TABLE maintenance_records (
    record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    maintenance_type VARCHAR(50),
    maintenance_date DATE,
    maintenance_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE vehicles (
    vehicle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    license_plate VARCHAR(15),
    model VARCHAR(50),
    manufacturer VARCHAR(50),
    year INT
);

CREATE TABLE environmental_impact (
    impact_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    emissions_rating INT,
    energy_consumption FLOAT,
    eco_friendly BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE MaintenanceRecords (
  record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  vehicle_id INT,
  maintenance_type TEXT,
  maintenance_date DATE,
  maintenance_notes TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE Vehicles (
  vehicle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  vehicle_type TEXT,
  manufacturer TEXT,
  year INT,
  capacity INT
)

CREATE TABLE MaintenanceTypes (
  type_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  type_name TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE Manufacturers (
  manufacturer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  manufacturer_name TEXT,
  headquarters_location TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE MaintenanceRecords (
    record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    maintenance_type VARCHAR(50),
    maintenance_date DATE,
    maintenance_cost DECIMAL(10, 2),
    maintenance_details TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Vehicles (
    vehicle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_type VARCHAR(50),
    manufacturer VARCHAR(50),
    purchase_date DATE,
    fuel_type VARCHAR(20),
    emission_standard VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE FuelConsumption (
    record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    fuel_type VARCHAR(20),
    fuel_liters DECIMAL(8, 2),
    fuel_cost DECIMAL(8, 2),
    fuel_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE EnvironmentalImpact (
    record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    carbon_footprint DECIMAL(10, 2),
    emission_level VARCHAR(20),
    inspection_date DATE,
    inspection_result VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE Inspections (
    inspection_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    inspection_date DATE,
    inspector_name VARCHAR(50),
    inspection_result VARCHAR(50),
    notes TEXT
);
